1
00:00:20,177 --> 00:00:23,600
King Bayinnaung, your Royal Uncle, has fallen ill.

2
00:00:23,830 --> 00:00:26,480
It is only fitting that we pay him a visit.

3
00:00:26,543 --> 00:00:29,703
He uses his own child as a shield. What is to stop me from doing the same?

4
00:00:29,817 --> 00:00:33,400
- I will not wed Princess Natshin Medaw.
- It is an order!

5
00:00:33,837 --> 00:00:37,361
Mingyi Swa must be made to realize what happens when he incurs my wrath,

6
00:00:37,517 --> 00:00:38,800
and what the consequences shall be.

7
00:00:39,250 --> 00:00:40,880
It is because you see that I am old, is it not?

8
00:00:40,970 --> 00:00:45,280
That you dared to arrange a match for Mingyi Swa without consulting me.

9
00:00:45,403 --> 00:00:48,080
If one is not resolute, how then can one hope to rule the people, Your Majesty?

10
00:00:48,237 --> 00:00:50,640
But if one hopes for this empire to live in peace and prosperity,

11
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:54,240
Then the throne of Hongsawadi cannot be entrusted to him.

12
00:00:54,403 --> 00:00:56,160
I shall have you succeed the Throne.

13
00:00:56,843 --> 00:00:59,520
And become the next King of Hongsawadi.

14
00:00:59,743 --> 00:01:01,040
If I ascend to the throne,

15
00:01:01,157 --> 00:01:04,280
will you rebel and refuse to be subject to Hongsawadi?

16
00:01:04,337 --> 00:01:07,080
If only you would let go, I would be free.

17
00:01:07,257 --> 00:01:09,880
Why have you done this to me, Father? How could you?

18
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:11,841
Grandfather.

19
00:01:12,881 --> 00:01:14,000
Mingyi Swa.

20
00:01:14,920 --> 00:01:16,360
Pay respects to Grandfather.

21
00:01:29,030 --> 00:01:30,720
The Kingdom of Hongsawadi has entered a new era.

22
00:01:36,903 --> 00:01:39,680
Crown Prince Jaisingh has ascended the throne,

23
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:50,360
taking the royal name

24
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:54,440
Hanthawaddy Hsinbyushin,

25
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:58,921
or as we commonly know him,

26
00:02:01,780 --> 00:02:03,120
King Nanda Bayin.

27
00:03:20,210 --> 00:03:21,120
How insolent.

28
00:03:22,890 --> 00:03:25,560
Which other lords of the vassal states have failed to appear?

29
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:28,640
King Maha Thammaracha has fallen ill,

30
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:31,641
and has thus appointed Prince Nares as his representative

31
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:34,560
to bring the tribute from Ayutthaya, Your Majesty.

32
00:03:36,590 --> 00:03:37,591
Who else?

33
00:03:38,737 --> 00:03:39,800
The Lord of Kung,

34
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:45,040
besides failing to come, has sent no representative,

35
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:48,640
nor has he delivered any tribute, Your Majesty.

36
00:03:55,190 --> 00:03:56,440
Kung is but a small city,

37
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:58,840
yet it dares to be so insolent.

38
00:03:59,130 --> 00:04:00,960
Perhaps there is someone pulling the strings behind them.

39
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:07,040
Has King Thado Minsaw, my Royal Uncle, arrived?

40
00:04:27,610 --> 00:04:29,841
With the lord of Kung in rebellion,

41
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:33,480
the new King of Hongsawadi

42
00:04:34,283 --> 00:04:36,720
will surely find no peace.

43
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:40,840
Before long, he will certainly raise an army to suppress them,

44
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,920
lest other cities follow their example.

45
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:48,240
Kung is situated far from Hongsawadi,

46
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:50,320
and moreover, it sits atop a mountain.

47
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:54,360
The elephants, horses, and troops of Hongsawadi

48
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:55,800
come from the lowlands

49
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,040
and are unaccustomed to the heights.

50
00:04:58,840 --> 00:05:00,240
To hope for victory

51
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:03,320
shall certainly be no easy feat.

52
00:05:07,257 --> 00:05:08,721
Originally, our City of Inwa

53
00:05:09,583 --> 00:05:12,122
held the duty of overseeing and controlling the northern provinces.

54
00:05:13,184 --> 00:05:15,185
Now that they have risen in rebellion,

55
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:19,840
Hongsawadi shall realize just how vital Inwa truly is.

56
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:29,141
My child, you are exceedingly clever.

57
00:05:30,221 --> 00:05:32,600
You planned to incite Kung to defect,

58
00:05:33,857 --> 00:05:35,680
so that not only must Hongsawadi plead for our aid,

59
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,480
but these provinces

60
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:41,560
must also rely on our protection.

61
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:46,361
It is, as they say, a victory on all fronts.

62
00:05:47,550 --> 00:05:49,241
War is inevitable.

63
00:05:50,140 --> 00:05:52,000
The time has come for me to wash away my shame.

64
00:06:00,450 --> 00:06:02,960
If Hongsawadi desires victory,

65
00:06:04,617 --> 00:06:06,840
Mingyi Swa

66
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:10,141
must come crawling to us.

67
00:07:29,370 --> 00:07:31,440
I thank you all

68
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:35,000
for gathering to perform the ritual of the water of allegiance today.

69
00:07:36,801 --> 00:07:40,001
Once this sacred oath has been taken,

70
00:07:41,510 --> 00:07:46,411
should anyone in the future harbor thoughts of betrayal against me,

71
00:07:47,611 --> 00:07:49,012
may they suffer a wretched death

72
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:55,000
and meet with utter ruin.

73
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:03,760
But for those who remain honest and loyal to me,

74
00:08:05,903 --> 00:08:09,280
may you find eternal happiness and prosperity.

75
00:08:11,030 --> 00:08:13,000
Long live the king.

76
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:37,760
Come, tonight we drink until dawn.

77
00:09:38,123 --> 00:09:39,160
There shall be no rest, and no sleep.

78
00:09:41,877 --> 00:09:42,878
Sure.

79
00:09:56,897 --> 00:09:57,898
From this day forward,

80
00:09:58,920 --> 00:10:00,840
I know not when we shall meet again.

81
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:04,781
On the winter solstice of every year,

82
00:10:06,081 --> 00:10:07,560
I shall await you, my brother, at the same place.

83
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:25,001
The land of Hongsawadi now belongs to my father.

84
00:10:27,800 --> 00:10:29,701
I am but the Crown Prince,

85
00:10:30,957 --> 00:10:32,200
and the promise I once made

86
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:35,760
to liberate Ayutthaya from its vassal status

87
00:10:41,870 --> 00:10:43,200
can no longer be fulfilled.

88
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,001
I understand.

89
00:11:03,837 --> 00:11:07,000
Nares, remember my words.

90
00:11:09,437 --> 00:11:10,600
In the days to come,

91
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:14,760
though Hongsawadi and Ayutthaya

92
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:17,480
may no longer stand as brother states,

93
00:11:21,443 --> 00:11:22,445
you,

94
00:11:28,557 --> 00:11:30,800
you shall always be my brother.

95
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:10,961
[Min A Htwe, daughter of Princess Suphankalaya]

96
00:12:11,090 --> 00:12:12,091
Min A Htwe,

97
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:18,440
We have not met for many a year, I could hardly recognize you.

98
00:12:19,523 --> 00:12:21,200
That is why I have brought her to pay her respects,

99
00:12:22,477 --> 00:12:25,700
so that should you meet, you will know you are kin.

100
00:12:28,230 --> 00:12:32,400
King Bayinnaung appointed Min A Htwe as the Myoza,

101
00:12:33,017 --> 00:12:35,400
to enjoy the revenues and taxes of Phitsanulok.

102
00:12:37,277 --> 00:12:40,160
Then why do you not take her to visit Phitsanulok?

103
00:12:43,650 --> 00:12:44,651
What did you say?

104
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:48,121
Are my child and I going to Phitsanulok?

105
00:12:48,170 --> 00:12:50,280
Or should we go to pay our respects to our grandparents in Ayutthaya?

106
00:13:04,463 --> 00:13:06,000
My child and I are hostages.

107
00:13:07,630 --> 00:13:09,400
Do you think this side would ever let us go?

108
00:13:10,336 --> 00:13:11,337
Before long,

109
00:13:12,160 --> 00:13:14,200
we shall inevitably come to a breaking point with Hongsawadi

110
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:18,281
Now that the glory of King Bayinnaung has reached its end, you will be in grave danger staying here.

111
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:21,120
If my child and I were to escape,

112
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:25,160
King Nanda Bayin would undoubtedly use this as a pretext

113
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:29,400
to march his armies against Phitsanulok and Ayutthaya.

114
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:31,640
- I...
- King Nanda Bayin has only just ascended the throne.

115
00:13:32,880 --> 00:13:34,760
His heart is filled with suspicion,

116
00:13:35,210 --> 00:13:37,280
fearing that cities great and small shall rebel.

117
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:39,700
Guard yourself well.

118
00:13:42,070 --> 00:13:43,280
From this moment forth,

119
00:13:43,823 --> 00:13:47,200
The flames of war shall spread far and wide. Mark my words.

120
00:13:56,160 --> 00:13:57,830
The King of Inwa has sent his reply,

121
00:13:58,083 --> 00:13:59,800
stating that he shall not aid in the war against Kung,

122
00:14:00,560 --> 00:14:03,160
and shall take no action until you offer a formal apology.

123
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:09,400
The King of Inwa is Grandfather’s half-brother,

124
00:14:11,280 --> 00:14:14,240
and his Chief Queen is Grandfather’s own sister.

125
00:14:16,910 --> 00:14:18,400
We are kin through two lineages.

126
00:14:19,280 --> 00:14:20,960
Yet, when the northern cities rebel,

127
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:23,280
if no aid is given,

128
00:14:25,777 --> 00:14:27,120
and he seizes the chance

129
00:14:27,763 --> 00:14:30,240
to use affairs of state to force my apology,

130
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:33,841
then I shall not do it.

131
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:36,000
The city of Inwa is of the utmost importance.

132
00:14:36,800 --> 00:14:39,801
If we cannot control Inwa, I shall never know a moment's peace.

133
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:43,001
You must go and offer your apologies to the King of Inwa,

134
00:14:43,560 --> 00:14:45,961
and enter into the royal marriage with Natshin Medaw.

135
00:14:46,133 --> 00:14:47,134
I shall not do it!

136
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:52,000
I harbor no feelings for her.

137
00:14:52,800 --> 00:14:56,400
- My heart has already been given to another!
- Mingyi Swa!

138
00:15:02,150 --> 00:15:03,800
I shall go to suppress the rebellion in Kung,

139
00:15:05,883 --> 00:15:07,440
and return with victory.

140
00:15:08,910 --> 00:15:10,480
If I succeed as stated,

141
00:15:11,680 --> 00:15:13,320
I shall request

142
00:15:13,810 --> 00:15:15,080
Princess Yaza Datu Kalaya,

143
00:15:15,357 --> 00:15:17,760
to be my Royal Consort.

144
00:15:36,837 --> 00:15:37,960
Not long thereafter,

145
00:15:38,800 --> 00:15:41,080
King Nanda Bayin commanded

146
00:15:41,157 --> 00:15:43,200
the Crown Prince Mingyi Swa

147
00:15:43,743 --> 00:15:45,640
to lead an army to attack Kung,

148
00:15:47,400 --> 00:15:48,401
with me

149
00:15:49,877 --> 00:15:53,440
leading the forces from Phitsanulok to reinforce them,

150
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:58,800
and Natshinnaung, the viceroy of Martaban,

151
00:16:00,720 --> 00:16:02,700
joining the campaign with his own troops.

152
00:16:04,343 --> 00:16:06,000
Kung is a plateau situated atop a hill.

153
00:16:07,310 --> 00:16:11,440
The path upward is narrow, and steep, while the rear is guarded by a towering cliff.

154
00:16:13,700 --> 00:16:15,240
Such strategic terrain is a fortress difficult to storm.

155
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:21,360
To rush headlong into the assault would be like fish swimming into a trap.

156
00:16:23,397 --> 00:16:24,500
It would surely lead us all to our deaths.

157
00:16:28,817 --> 00:16:31,240
We have three armies at our disposal. We must take turns in the assault.

158
00:16:31,920 --> 00:16:34,400
Only by striking when they are caught off guard can we hope to break through.

159
00:17:15,800 --> 00:17:16,960
What is the matter?

160
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:31,401
It is truly because of me

161
00:17:33,480 --> 00:17:35,000
that you all must endure such hardship.

162
00:17:39,227 --> 00:17:42,760
Your Highness, you fight with all your heart for the sake of my elder sister.

163
00:17:43,520 --> 00:17:45,960
As the true younger brother of Yaza Datu Kalaya,

164
00:17:46,520 --> 00:17:48,200
I, too, shall aid you with every fiber of my being.

165
00:17:51,080 --> 00:17:54,160
In this case, defeat in this battle is not an option.

166
00:17:55,840 --> 00:17:58,560
If we cannot lose, then victory is our only path, is it not?

167
00:17:59,503 --> 00:18:00,240
Yes, Your Highness.

168
00:18:11,643 --> 00:18:15,040
Rest your heart, Brother. In this battle of Kung,

169
00:18:15,810 --> 00:18:17,041
victory is our only destiny.

170
00:18:26,577 --> 00:18:29,480
Our three armies shall divide their duties.

171
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:31,520
The army of Mingyi Swa

172
00:18:32,017 --> 00:18:35,280
shall engage the Kung forces during the light of day.

173
00:18:45,557 --> 00:18:46,558
Draw.

174
00:18:52,457 --> 00:18:53,458
Shoot!

175
00:19:02,923 --> 00:19:03,924
Watch out!

176
00:19:05,723 --> 00:19:06,724
Go!

177
00:19:32,157 --> 00:19:36,200
Meanwhile, my army shall scale the cliffs

178
00:19:36,540 --> 00:19:37,600
and ascend from the rear,

179
00:19:38,360 --> 00:19:41,520
unseen by the forces of Kung.

180
00:20:22,810 --> 00:20:23,960
Under the cover of night,

181
00:20:24,720 --> 00:20:27,800
Natshinnaung shall lead the reinforcement troops to launch an assault,

182
00:20:29,897 --> 00:20:33,040
allowing Kung soldiers no moment of respite.

183
00:20:38,410 --> 00:20:40,211
Quick, everyone! Help extinguish the flames!

184
00:20:45,510 --> 00:20:46,920
Please retreat first, Your Majesty.

185
00:20:46,930 --> 00:20:48,400
We shall hold the line here ourselves.

186
00:20:49,503 --> 00:20:50,504
It is too late!

187
00:21:40,450 --> 00:21:43,500
The battle of Kung concluded in victory,

188
00:21:45,440 --> 00:21:47,600
but the internal conflict within Hongsawadi

189
00:21:49,760 --> 00:21:51,120
has only just begun to erupt.

190
00:22:03,497 --> 00:22:07,750
The Crown Prince has triumphed and seized the Lord of Kung

191
00:22:08,930 --> 00:22:11,360
This is most auspicious news, Your Majesty.

192
00:22:13,520 --> 00:22:16,960
Victory is ours this time, yet the next remains uncertain.

193
00:22:18,760 --> 00:22:21,640
If the King of Inwa continues to back the northern cities

194
00:22:21,743 --> 00:22:23,080
in their rebellion against us,

195
00:22:24,203 --> 00:22:26,600
Hongsawadi shall be condemned to eternal warfare.

196
00:22:28,770 --> 00:22:29,771
And what then?

197
00:22:30,650 --> 00:22:32,170
Instead of waging war,

198
00:22:33,760 --> 00:22:37,803
Is it not better to find a way to sever the roots of conflict, Your Majesty?

199
00:22:45,277 --> 00:22:48,920
By your grace, we have returned triumphant from the battlefield.

200
00:22:49,700 --> 00:22:53,040
And we have captured the Lord of Kung, as per your royal command.

201
00:22:54,240 --> 00:22:55,390
Drag him out!

202
00:22:55,643 --> 00:22:56,644
Let go of me!

203
00:22:59,250 --> 00:23:00,251
Let go of me!

204
00:23:08,880 --> 00:23:10,360
Lord of Kung.

205
00:23:11,477 --> 00:23:13,400
You dared to commit treason against me.

206
00:23:14,810 --> 00:23:19,080
Guards, take him away to be beheaded and his head displayed on a pike.

207
00:23:19,560 --> 00:23:22,440
Let this be a warning to all other vassal lords, lest they follow his example.

208
00:23:24,190 --> 00:23:25,191
Let go of me!

209
00:23:26,597 --> 00:23:27,598
Let go of me!

210
00:23:29,637 --> 00:23:30,638
Let go of me!

211
00:23:30,638 --> 00:23:32,040
I said let go!

212
00:23:34,290 --> 00:23:35,291
Let go of me!

213
00:23:38,997 --> 00:23:40,160
Crown Prince,

214
00:23:41,243 --> 00:23:43,440
your victory over Kung is most commendable.

215
00:23:44,280 --> 00:23:46,000
It brings great joy and pride to our kingdom.

216
00:23:47,400 --> 00:23:51,300
As your reward, I bestow upon you half of the treasures of Kung.

217
00:23:51,963 --> 00:23:52,964
The other half

218
00:23:53,500 --> 00:23:56,200
divided equally between Prince Nares and Prince Natshinnaung.

219
00:24:00,361 --> 00:24:02,000
- Your royal grace is boundless, Your Majesty.
- Your royal grace is boundless, Your Majesty.

220
00:24:07,657 --> 00:24:09,761
Crown Prince Mingyi Swa,

221
00:24:12,640 --> 00:24:16,641
As commander, you have achieved your first victory upon my soil.

222
00:24:18,117 --> 00:24:21,520
I shall grant you the Royal Consort as your reward.

223
00:24:25,403 --> 00:24:26,720
I humbly accept,

224
00:24:28,404 --> 00:24:31,405
with the deepest gratitude for Your Majesty's boundless grace.

225
00:24:32,983 --> 00:24:34,040
Ministers and officials,

226
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:38,160
Task every department to begin preparations.

227
00:24:39,240 --> 00:24:41,961
I shall hold a grand royal wedding

228
00:24:43,640 --> 00:24:46,360
for Crown Prince Mingyi Swa

229
00:24:47,880 --> 00:24:51,881
and Princess Natshin Medaw of Inwa, within the coming month.

230
00:25:27,283 --> 00:25:28,600
Why have you done this?

231
00:25:30,977 --> 00:25:33,360
For the stability of Hongsawadi.

232
00:25:38,800 --> 00:25:40,400
But I have told you before,

233
00:25:42,010 --> 00:25:43,280
that I do not love her.

234
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:47,121
But the northern provinces shall remain at peace,

235
00:25:48,080 --> 00:25:49,400
and you will no longer have to go to war.

236
00:25:53,840 --> 00:25:55,841
Do you not hate war so?

237
00:25:56,957 --> 00:25:58,280
You have no desire to kill,

238
00:25:59,240 --> 00:26:01,720
nor to see your subjects suffer and die.

239
00:26:02,803 --> 00:26:04,810
Or is it that for one woman,

240
00:26:05,597 --> 00:26:07,560
the lives of your soldiers no longer matter?

241
00:26:14,977 --> 00:26:16,120
In the past,

242
00:26:17,760 --> 00:26:19,400
I have been far too lenient with you.

243
00:26:21,410 --> 00:26:23,760
But this time, it is a Royal Command.

244
00:26:24,120 --> 00:26:27,600
Before the Great Assembly, you shall not defy my word.

245
00:26:30,520 --> 00:26:31,560
In the past,

246
00:26:34,520 --> 00:26:39,120
I pleaded with you as a son pleads with his father.

247
00:26:44,640 --> 00:26:49,000
But if Your Majesty speaks by Royal Command,

248
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:54,280
then I must humbly take My leave.

249
00:27:19,320 --> 00:27:23,160
Your Highness, please show Your Mercy.

250
00:27:24,563 --> 00:27:25,564
What is the matter?

251
00:27:26,010 --> 00:27:29,960
They have already come to escort Princess Yaza Datu Kalaya away.

252
00:27:57,510 --> 00:27:58,511
Stop!

253
00:27:59,240 --> 00:28:00,241
I said stop!

254
00:28:11,897 --> 00:28:12,898
Royal Aunt.

255
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:15,280
Where are you going.

256
00:28:23,730 --> 00:28:27,240
I have been ordered to Martaban

257
00:28:28,720 --> 00:28:29,721
to build a temple,

258
00:28:30,617 --> 00:28:33,170
to make merit for the soul of my late father.

259
00:28:35,040 --> 00:28:36,600
Only when it is finished shall I return.

260
00:28:41,023 --> 00:28:44,360
My sister has never stepped foot outside the palace since she was born.

261
00:28:44,920 --> 00:28:46,921
to order her to Martaban now

262
00:28:47,183 --> 00:28:49,640
is no different from exiling her to death.

263
00:29:05,600 --> 00:29:06,760
You do not have to go.

264
00:29:16,510 --> 00:29:17,511
Father!

265
00:29:19,960 --> 00:29:21,200
I yield!

266
00:29:24,870 --> 00:29:25,871
Father!

267
00:29:28,437 --> 00:29:29,720
I give in!

268
00:29:33,680 --> 00:29:34,681
Father!

269
00:29:36,863 --> 00:29:40,117
I yield! Do you hear me?

270
00:29:40,783 --> 00:29:42,320
I yield!

271
00:29:49,697 --> 00:29:51,640
I yield!

272
00:30:36,083 --> 00:30:37,084
Brother.

273
00:30:41,743 --> 00:30:42,744
Brother.

274
00:30:46,930 --> 00:30:48,200
I must depart now.

275
00:31:05,600 --> 00:31:08,720
If you can endure it no longer, then come with me.

276
00:31:10,183 --> 00:31:12,417
Within the walls of Phitsanulok, I am the sovereign.

277
00:31:13,003 --> 00:31:14,920
I shall not allow anyone to harm you, Brother.

278
00:31:22,330 --> 00:31:23,331
My brother.

279
00:31:27,783 --> 00:31:30,120
Not even the walls of Phitsanulok,

280
00:31:40,483 --> 00:31:42,520
nor even the walls of Ayutthaya,

281
00:31:47,120 --> 00:31:49,800
can hope to stand against the King of Hongsawadi.

282
00:32:54,050 --> 00:32:55,051
Begin!

283
00:33:11,203 --> 00:33:12,204
Run!

284
00:33:15,077 --> 00:33:16,120
The fallen one, get out!

285
00:33:16,477 --> 00:33:17,520
Hurry!

286
00:33:18,470 --> 00:33:19,471
Go!

287
00:33:19,906 --> 00:33:20,640
Quicker!

288
00:33:24,417 --> 00:33:25,418
Hurry!

289
00:33:28,330 --> 00:33:29,331
Go!

290
00:33:38,450 --> 00:33:39,451
Shoot!

291
00:33:54,683 --> 00:33:56,520
Someone told me that

292
00:33:57,840 --> 00:34:01,760
not even the walls of Phitsanulok nor the walls of Ayutthaya

293
00:34:02,480 --> 00:34:05,080
could withstand the army of the King of Hongsawadi.

294
00:34:06,817 --> 00:34:08,400
With an army of hundreds of thousands,

295
00:34:09,490 --> 00:34:11,600
if every man threw but a single stone at the wall,

296
00:34:12,560 --> 00:34:14,700
it would crumble before long.

297
00:34:15,520 --> 00:34:18,920
But we shall not wait for death behind these walls.

298
00:34:20,237 --> 00:34:24,481
If the army of Hongsawadi invades, we shall go out to face them.

299
00:34:25,803 --> 00:34:28,160
I seek men of great skill to stand by my side,

300
00:34:29,390 --> 00:34:32,320
the finest, the fastest,

301
00:34:33,200 --> 00:34:36,000
the most enduring, and the bravest.

302
00:34:36,680 --> 00:34:40,000
You all shall fight shoulder to shoulder with me

303
00:34:40,640 --> 00:34:41,920
as my elite warriors.

304
00:34:42,240 --> 00:34:43,920
The elite warriors of prince dam!

305
00:34:44,360 --> 00:34:45,600
The elite warriors of prince dam!

306
00:34:45,920 --> 00:34:47,520
The elite warriors of prince dam!

307
00:34:48,040 --> 00:34:51,240
The elite warriors of prince dam!

308
00:34:51,640 --> 00:34:52,983
The elite warriors of prince dam!

309
00:34:53,110 --> 00:34:56,200
For me, freedom

310
00:34:56,840 --> 00:34:58,800
is within my reach.

311
00:34:59,841 --> 00:35:01,600
but for Mingyi Swa,

312
00:35:02,397 --> 00:35:03,520
Freedom...

313
00:35:04,840 --> 00:35:06,041
has slipped through his hands.

314
00:35:52,317 --> 00:35:53,318
Brother.

315
00:35:59,550 --> 00:36:00,800
This marriage

316
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:04,400
is for the benefit of Inwa and Hongsawadi.

317
00:36:06,880 --> 00:36:08,281
I honor you, my lady,

318
00:36:10,120 --> 00:36:12,280
for sacrificing yourself for the sake of the kingdom.

319
00:36:14,760 --> 00:36:15,761
but since it is so,

320
00:36:17,080 --> 00:36:19,760
sleeping together would be forced upon both sides,

321
00:36:20,890 --> 00:36:22,000
which is most improper.

322
00:36:26,710 --> 00:36:29,100
I invite you to rest at your leisure;

323
00:36:30,890 --> 00:36:32,500
Ishall retire to my own quarters.

324
00:36:34,763 --> 00:36:36,764
Please listen to me first.

325
00:36:45,910 --> 00:36:46,911
It is true

326
00:36:48,870 --> 00:36:53,640
that I do not have the slightest affection for you, my Lord.

327
00:36:55,560 --> 00:36:56,561
But…

328
00:37:14,665 --> 00:37:16,800
since we are now wed,

329
00:37:19,600 --> 00:37:22,040
I am officially

330
00:37:24,360 --> 00:37:25,361
your wife.

331
00:37:27,997 --> 00:37:32,520
Whatever is due, whatever is mine to have,

332
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:38,520
I must have it.

333
00:37:44,040 --> 00:37:45,041
Everything.

334
00:37:47,041 --> 00:37:48,342
No matter what it may be.

335
00:38:47,400 --> 00:38:49,480
With you all attacking with such a raucous noise,

336
00:38:49,890 --> 00:38:50,920
wherever you go, you go only to die in vain.

337
00:38:52,760 --> 00:38:53,661
Start again.

338
00:38:53,730 --> 00:38:54,731
Yes, Your Highness.

339
00:39:04,303 --> 00:39:05,880
Did you see the faces of those two?

340
00:39:07,080 --> 00:39:08,720
they look like they might be frightened, Your Highness.

341
00:39:11,410 --> 00:39:12,920
Wow, Muy.

342
00:39:13,083 --> 00:39:15,360
- It is as if the Buddha has come to our rescue.
- Hey!

343
00:39:15,680 --> 00:39:19,040
What Buddha brings booze to save you? Your mouth will land you in hell.

344
00:39:20,080 --> 00:39:22,680
Hell is where I am headed, for sure.

345
00:39:23,160 --> 00:39:24,920
Let me soak my soul in liquor first.

346
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:28,000
Your Highness.

347
00:39:32,443 --> 00:39:35,280
It is late into the night. What are you doing here?

348
00:39:38,270 --> 00:39:41,381
My father sent me in haste to report an urgent matter.

349
00:39:42,640 --> 00:39:43,641
It was last month.

350
00:39:43,783 --> 00:39:46,240
Father found a great herd of wild elephants with magnificent tusks.

351
00:39:47,000 --> 00:39:48,840
so, he tracked them all the way to Kamphaeng Phet.

352
00:39:49,937 --> 00:39:50,720
And then what?

353
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:55,000
So he ran into the Hongsawadi.

354
00:40:13,443 --> 00:40:14,450
What is that sound?

355
00:40:47,963 --> 00:40:48,964
What has happened?

356
00:40:49,537 --> 00:40:52,960
The peasants were working too slowly, so I taught them a lesson, Your Highness.

357
00:40:59,320 --> 00:41:02,200
Oh, they are all dead.

358
00:41:03,520 --> 00:41:05,000
You were too hasty and impulsive.

359
00:41:06,680 --> 00:41:09,040
Now, who is left to dig the earth and build the road?

360
00:41:12,160 --> 00:41:13,161
You all,

361
00:41:14,161 --> 00:41:15,403
take the bodies and bury them far away.

362
00:41:16,030 --> 00:41:17,481
Bury them well, lest the tigers catch their scent.

363
00:41:18,231 --> 00:41:19,232
Yes, Your Highness.

364
00:41:19,643 --> 00:41:20,920
Return to Hongsawadi.

365
00:41:21,457 --> 00:41:24,001
Report that the peasants recruited have all died of jungle fever.

366
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:28,400
I am following the Royal Command to complete the road to Ayutthaya with haste.

367
00:41:29,077 --> 00:41:32,880
If new men are not sent immediately and the work is delayed,

368
00:41:33,043 --> 00:41:35,480
I shall petition the King to punish everyone, without exception.

369
00:41:36,743 --> 00:41:37,880
As you command, Your Highness.

370
00:41:45,480 --> 00:41:47,481
Does Father also know of the road’s construction?

371
00:41:48,163 --> 00:41:49,164
Yes, he does.

372
00:41:51,570 --> 00:41:53,800
For it is known that Minye Kyawswa is most cruel.

373
00:41:55,560 --> 00:41:58,920
The Shan people conscripted to build the road often attempt to escape.

374
00:41:59,640 --> 00:42:01,120
Some survive, while others perish.

375
00:42:02,830 --> 00:42:04,983
Not a few have managed to survive and reach Ayutthaya.

376
00:42:08,157 --> 00:42:11,720
Not only the road, Hongsawadi is also building granaries.

377
00:42:11,910 --> 00:42:14,721
They have begun to stockpile provisions, surely preparing for a great war.

378
00:42:16,030 --> 00:42:18,080
That is why Father ordered me to come and find you.

379
00:42:21,560 --> 00:42:23,400
This year, I have aged significantly.

380
00:42:24,360 --> 00:42:26,840
Furthermore, he suffers from illness almost every day.

381
00:42:29,920 --> 00:42:33,680
Hongsawadi likely reckons that he does not have much longer to live.

382
00:42:34,837 --> 00:42:35,838
Father.

383
00:42:36,920 --> 00:42:38,880
All men are born to die.

384
00:42:40,390 --> 00:42:41,720
But if Father must pass,

385
00:42:43,550 --> 00:42:45,560
I pray it does not bring hardship upon the Kingdom.

386
00:42:47,140 --> 00:42:50,520
Khao, you must carry my words.

387
00:42:53,320 --> 00:42:54,321
Yes, Your Majesty.

388
00:42:55,440 --> 00:42:58,641
Nanda Bayin is deeply suspicious of your older brother.

389
00:43:00,417 --> 00:43:01,600
If I passes away,

390
00:43:02,840 --> 00:43:06,080
he will likely appoint someone else to sit upon the throne of Ayutthaya.

391
00:43:07,663 --> 00:43:10,880
How could that be? Nares would never allow it, nor would I.

392
00:43:12,520 --> 00:43:14,240
Nanda Bayin is well aware of this,

393
00:43:15,320 --> 00:43:17,321
which is why he is preparing for a major war.

394
00:43:19,717 --> 00:43:21,760
Go and consult with Dam,

395
00:43:23,463 --> 00:43:25,120
should I pass away

396
00:43:27,017 --> 00:43:29,280
and he marches his army to seize Ayutthaya,

397
00:43:30,377 --> 00:43:32,240
what will the two of you do?

398
00:43:44,400 --> 00:43:46,700
Ayutthaya has lost nearly all of its skilled men.

399
00:43:49,297 --> 00:43:52,960
Father and I must rebuild the army,

400
00:43:54,000 --> 00:43:55,200
yet it is still not as strong as it once was.

401
00:43:57,790 --> 00:43:58,791
And what of things here?

402
00:44:00,320 --> 00:44:03,520
The soldiers here possess singular skill,

403
00:44:04,417 --> 00:44:05,710
but our numbers remain far too few.

404
00:44:06,430 --> 00:44:08,440
They will not suffice should we have to face a great army.

405
00:44:13,497 --> 00:44:15,410
In that case, we must make haste to find more men to reinforce our army.

406
00:44:26,640 --> 00:44:27,641
Right.

407
00:44:29,400 --> 00:44:30,600
Speaking of which, I just remembered.

408
00:44:32,263 --> 00:44:33,700
I have a gift for you.

409
00:44:35,003 --> 00:44:38,004
I guarantee you will surely be pleased.

410
00:44:56,400 --> 00:44:57,920
Is this the thing you said?

411
00:44:58,760 --> 00:44:59,761
Yes.

412
00:45:26,490 --> 00:45:28,280
This sword is forged from Nam Phi steel, Your Highness.

413
00:45:50,870 --> 00:45:51,880
This one is good.

414
00:45:54,803 --> 00:45:58,240
Your Majesty, the Nam Phi steel sword is the supreme blade.

415
00:45:59,103 --> 00:46:01,360
The steel is tough, light, yet durable.

416
00:46:01,960 --> 00:46:04,720
Furthermore, it possesses supernatural powers, protecting the wielder from harm

417
00:46:05,670 --> 00:46:06,840
and cleansing them of dark spells and curses.

418
00:46:08,077 --> 00:46:10,520
It is extremely difficult to forge even a single one.

419
00:46:11,510 --> 00:46:12,511
I already know that.

420
00:46:14,400 --> 00:46:15,440
But who are you?

421
00:46:16,637 --> 00:46:17,760
Are you a sword merchant?

422
00:46:20,957 --> 00:46:23,560
He is Phra Chai Buri, formerly known as Duang.

423
00:46:24,670 --> 00:46:25,800
He is a man who seeks knowledge in warfare,

424
00:46:27,560 --> 00:46:28,600
and possesses great expertise regarding weaponry.

425
00:46:30,277 --> 00:46:31,440
I have therefore invited him to come and assist you.

426
00:46:32,237 --> 00:46:33,238
Good.

427
00:46:34,417 --> 00:46:36,080
You brought them to me, a good man

428
00:46:37,297 --> 00:46:38,298
and a fine sword.

429
00:46:38,983 --> 00:46:39,984
Many thanks.

430
00:46:43,320 --> 00:46:44,321
Phet, Sri,

431
00:46:46,160 --> 00:46:48,161
we are about to gain another great warrior.

432
00:46:51,000 --> 00:46:52,001
Yes, Your Highness.

433
00:46:54,360 --> 00:46:56,361
It is Your Majesty’s grace.

434
00:47:15,720 --> 00:47:17,280
I have therefore gathered men,

435
00:47:20,437 --> 00:47:22,300
stockpiled weapons and provisions,

436
00:47:25,503 --> 00:47:26,600
and made ready

437
00:47:27,477 --> 00:47:31,640
for the next war with Hongsawadi.

438
00:47:41,080 --> 00:47:43,440
Now we have cause to visit Hongsawadi.

439
00:47:43,760 --> 00:47:46,040
If they crave war, let them have their fill.

440
00:47:46,400 --> 00:47:49,720
Now that Grandfather has passed, the provinces have indeed grown defiant, just as you said.

441
00:47:50,070 --> 00:47:52,920
How could I deal with them all by myself?

442
00:47:53,160 --> 00:47:55,520
Return and inform the King of Hongsawadi,

443
00:47:57,731 --> 00:48:02,120
shall lead my army at once to join the war against Inwa.

444
00:48:02,360 --> 00:48:06,520
This time, if that captive joins the battle, I will have my rematch.

445
00:48:06,817 --> 00:48:08,320
The time has come, Your Reverence,

446
00:48:08,650 --> 00:48:11,440
for me to be free.
